                throws org.xml.sax.SAXException,
                       java.io.FileNotFoundException,

        Processes OSM data to create a network file
        Parameters:
        osmData - The OSM data XML file
        standardizer - The network standardizer to use (depends of your needs)
        converter - The network converter to use (depends of your needs)
        css - The CSS file to use
        exporter - The exporter to use (depends of wanted output format)
        output - The output file
        Returns:
        True if process worked
        Throws:
        org.xml.sax.SAXException - Error during OSM data parsing
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - If given CSS doesn't exist
        java.io.IOException - If an error occurs during export
        java.lang.Exception - If an error occurs during network conversion
